 state. The traditional approach based on the Average Run Length,\nempirically computed via a Monte Carlo simulation, was adopted.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 3 Jul 2015 22:28:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-07-07"}
